metadata.name: Self - Feeling Energy
metadata.description:
“Self - Feeling Energy”, is a derivative of Rik Oostenbroek’s awesome piece “Self”.

My aim is to give the idea that you are thinking, feeling, or smelling something beautiful. The energy of the entire face, skin and brain feels and vibrates for itself.

1/1 
3D Animation, using Blender 3D - 3800 × 3600 px
